query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('actionscript',
'conv-neural-network',
'deadlock',
'expression',
'grid',
'javamail',
'locale',
'lstm',
'overflow',
'pdfbox',
'python-2.x',
'qt4',
'signals',
'streaming');
